git submodule init
git submodule update
composer.phar update
cd vendor/bin
./classmap_generator.php -l ../../app -w -o ../../app/config/autoload_classmap.php

Any time you want the latest version of the submodule(s) do git submodule update
Best practice, don't make modifications to the submodule, don't use git pull in the submodule

classmap_generator needs to be run anytime a new class file is added to the app.
